headline: NTRS Q3 Deep Dive: Margin Expansion and Strategic Focus Amid Industry Fee Pressure
summary: Financial services company Northern Trust (NASDAQ:NTRS) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 3.2% year on year to $2.03 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.29 per share was 1.7% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
